            <div type="transcript" id="J1433">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>How brittle are the Piers</l>
                    <l>On which our Faith doth tread --</l>
                    <l>No Bridge below doth totter so --</l>
                    <l>Yet none hath such a Crowd.</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It is as old as God</l>
                    <l>Indeed -- 'twas built by him --</l>
                    <l>He sent his Son to test the Plank,</l>
                    <l>And he pronounced it firm.</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
